text: Vera Aleksandrovna Klimovich (born 29 April 1988 Minsk) is a Belarusian volleyball player. She competed at the 2015 Women's European Volleyball Championship, 2017 Women's European Volleyball Championship, 2019 Women's European Volleyball Championship, and 2019 Women's European Volleyball League winning a bronze medal. On club level she plays for VB Casalmaggiore, Volley 2002 Forlì, Maccabi XT Haifa, and Hämeenlinnan Lentopallokerho. == References == Category:1988 births Category:Belarusian volleyball players Category:Living people
